      "acceptanceCriteria": "Commercial FEA solvers (Ansys Mechanical 2022 R1) used in this study must hold current ISO 9001 certification and vendor-supplied V&V documentation covering linear-static and contact analysis modules. Internal QA records must confirm version control and regression test passage prior to analysis runs.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R1 is ISO 9001 certified. Vendor V&V documentation covering linear-static, contact, and nonlinear material modules was reviewed. Internal version control logs and regression test suite passage records were confirmed prior to each analysis run. Achieved level 3 exceeds the required level 2 for a Medium model-risk context."
